trans-unit.source: Represents the license transform algorithm used to normalize XrML licenses for signatures.
trans-unit.target: Representerer lisens transformering algoritmen som brukes til normaliseres XrML lisenser for signaturer.

trans-unit.source: The XmlLicenseTransform class represents the license transform algorithm as defined in the MPEG Rights Extension Language (MPEG REL).
trans-unit.target: Klassen XmlLicenseTransform representerer lisens transformering algoritmen som er definert i MPEG rettigheter utvidelsen språket (MPEG REL).

trans-unit.source: Use the XmlLicenseTransform class to transform XrML licenses for signatures.
trans-unit.target: Bruk klassen XmlLicenseTransform vil gjøre XrML lisenser for signaturer.

trans-unit.source: The Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) that describes the XmlLicenseTransform class is defined by the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.XmlLicenseTransformUrl> field.
trans-unit.target: Uniform Resource Identifier (URI) som beskriver XmlLicenseTransform klassen er definert av den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.XmlLicenseTransformUrl>felt.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.XmlLicenseTransformUrl>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform> object uses an <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.IRelDecryptor> interface to decrypt `<encryptedGrant>` elements from the current `<license>` element.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform>objekt bruker en <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.IRelDecryptor>grensesnittet dekryptere `<encryptedGrant>` elementer fra gjeldende `<license>` element.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.IRelDecryptor> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.XmlLicenseTransform>
